cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with unsupervised learning of sentence embeddings. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it introduces a multitask objective into unsupervised learning. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with deriving meaningful data representations from vast amounts of unlabeled data. It could also be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as sentence embeddings are often used as features in image captioning tasks. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with unsupervised learning using neural networks.
